column2: ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. OBJECTIVE HAS BEEN CLEARED. OVER.
ALPHA TO BRAVO. WE ARE DONE HERE. REQUESTING EXTRACTION. OVER.
ALPHA GET READY. LANDING ZONE IN SIGHT. OVER.
GOOD LUCK ALPHA. GIVE 'EM HELL. BRAVO OUT.
BRAVO TO ALPHA. GET READY FOR EXTRACTION. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. COPY THAT. CALL BRAVO. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
